# state/ Directory

## Purpose
Runtime working directory for artifacts, verification reports, and temp outputs.

## Subdirectories
```
state/
├── artifacts/    # Generated HTML, screenshots, PDFs
├── verify/       # Playwright verification JSON reports
└── sessions/     # Per-session working files (optional)
```

## Notes
- All contents here are generated — not committed to repo
- Artifacts should be downloadable by the user
- Reports are for structured output (JSON) to be parsed by the skill
- Cleanup policy: artifacts older than 7 days can be purged (Phase 2)
